rComments: He is the best professor ever to walk this very large campus.

This course was a lot of work, but if you're willing to put in the effort and reach out for help, you can do really well and learn a lot. Rule is very knowledgeable and approachable. As a class, you choose what research project to undertake; and complete it from beginning to end. Overall great learning experience.
You will learn a lot in this class but find it very hard to get a good grade

Prof. Rule started off as being my favourite Prof. but quickly turned into my worst nightmare. He bases marks in the class based on how much he likes the person. Ever since I disputed an error that he made in marking (which he didn't fix), he has made it almost impossible for me to get a decent grade. Don't take this class if you respect yourself.
Professor Rule made the class very enjoyable, it was interesting and interactive. One of the best, if not the best PSY course I have taken. + I learned a lot about cultural psychology.
Great prof! Very enthusiastic and knowledgeable.  Participation in the course is a must, but Prof. Rule makes it easy to speak up.  Overall, an excellent prof for an excellent course!
